Features:
---------
  * High-level and low-level network and system diagnostics, statistics and control.
  * Lightweight. Low memory and CPU usage.
  * Loosely-coupled, allowing database, web application, daemon and collectors to all reside on different servers.
  * Written to use commodity hardware, programming languages, protocols and database systems.

